The boy is due to appear in the Strand Magistrates Court today on a charge of murder. CAPE TOWN - A 12-year-old boy is expected to appear in the Strand Magistrates Court today on a charge of murder.He's implicated in the death of an 11-year-old boy, who was stabbed near home on Saturday evening.The boy was arrested soon after the stabbing and later placed in his mother's care. The motive for the stabbing is unclear.(Edited by Shimoney Regter)